comments: Dunn (CHI) intentionally makes foot to ball contact.
Dunn (CHI) and George (LAC) engage and disengage prior to the inbound pass.
Shamet (LAC) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Dunn's (CHI) path.
Carter Jr. (CHI) establishes himself in a legal picking position in George's (LAC) path.
Dunn (CHI) makes contact with George's (LAC) arm during his driving shot attempt.
Carter Jr. (CHI) establishes himself in a legal picking position in George's (LAC) path and slightly extends his arms as he releases from the pick.
Shamet (LAC) makes marginal contact with Dunn's (CHI) arm as he cleanly dislodges the ball.
After making contact with the ball, Dunn (CHI) makes marginal contact with Harkless' (LAC) arm.
Shamet (LAC) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Dunn's (CHI) path.
Dunn (CHI) makes contact with George's (LAC) body that affects his upward shooting motion.
As Dunn (CHI) secures the rebound, Harrell (LAC) makes marginal contact to his arm.
Shamet (LAC) makes contact with LaVine's (CHI) arm after the gather affecting his ability to maintain possession of the ball during his driving shot attempt.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Replay review of the play determined the ball last touches LaVine (CHI) before going out of bounds.
George (LAC) and Dunn (CHI) engage and disengage off-ball.
Harrell (LAC) makes marginal contact with Carter Jr. (CHI) as he attempts to retrieve the rebound.
George (LAC) commits a take foul on LaVine (CHI).
Harrell (LAC) makes contact with LaVine's (CHI) body during his driving shot attempt.
Harrell (LAC) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Dunn's (CHI) path.
